# - Try to find the Catralibraries library
# Once done this will define
#
# CATRALIBRARIES_FOUND - system has the CatraLibraries library
# CATRALIBRARIES_INCLUDE_DIR - the CatraLibraries include directory
# CATRALIBRARIES_LIBRARIES - The libraries needed to use CatraLibraries
